1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,420
Anyị nwere ozi kachasị ọhụrụ ugbu a na Sydney ebe ndị uwe ojii abụọ gbapụrụ mmerụ ahụ siri ike mgbe

2
00:00:04,420 --> 00:00:08,000
Ụgbọala ndị uwe ojii dara ma tụgharịa n'ebe ọdịda anyanwụ obodo ahụ.

3
00:00:08,000 --> 00:00:12,000
Ọ dakwasịrị n'elu ụlọ ya na Gilford n'ihe dị ka elekere ise na ọkara nke ụtụtụ a mgbe ndị uwe ojii si Auburn

4
00:00:12,000 --> 00:00:16,480
ha na-azaghachi akụkọ banyere ndị ikom na-eme ihe na-enyo enyo n'ụgbọala.

5
00:00:16,480 --> 00:00:18,960
A na-enyocha ndị uwe ojii abụọ ahụ ugbu a n'ụlọ ọgwụ.

